{"tid":2082412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果： 觀塘抗爭展覽獲批後突幔取消 區議員今發現場地被鎖 黑警用Cam 拍底逗留市民","createTime":"2020-06-28T04:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T08:42:21.000Z","uid":22556,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a1e2856003c82e7846254dc449e8f9a27e8eefc4","tid":2082412,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"為了在「深藍重鎮」油塘區反映抗爭運動的真相，與假新聞抗衡，油塘區議員龔振祺原定今日（28日）聯同10位藝術家，在油塘社區會堂舉行《第一年的故事》抗爭藝術展覽，惟借用場所申請在兩日前，突然遭民政事務署無理取消。龔振祺今日嘗試如常到會堂領取場地，不過大門被鎖上無法內進。龔指會另外借用場地，期望重新舉辦展覽。<br />\n<br />\n龔振祺原本打算如常進入社區會堂，但發現大門已被鎖上，無法內進。今早大約上午9點45分，已有3名軍裝警員到油塘社區會堂外視察，並拍攝在場逗留的市民，不過並無留守附近戒備。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200628/BRYS76A2S6MUVEYLZEOY6INLCQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200628%2FBRYS76A2S6MUVEYLZEOY6INLCQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=M%2BdtfvqsQfe3pFkx%2BxFNtApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=204c8b35\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200628%2FBRYS76A2S6MUVEYLZEOY6INLCQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=15632411\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200628/BRYS76A2S6MUVEYLZEOY6INLCQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"df8400d96d76e42e59405ea5ca949b8ace24cf8f","tid":2082412,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1e2856003c82e7846254dc449e8f9a27e8eefc4","tid":2082412,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"為了在「深藍重鎮」油塘區反映抗爭運動的真相，與假新聞抗衡，油塘區議員龔振祺原定今日（28日）聯同10位藝術家，在油塘社區會堂舉行《第一年的故事》抗爭藝術展覽，惟借用場所申請